1
00:00:00,260 --> 00:00:01,820
This is every day for them.

2
00:00:02,400 --> 00:00:03,820
This affects you, too.

3
00:00:04,860 --> 00:00:07,680
Well, with your grades, I'm not too
worried.

4
00:00:07,880 --> 00:00:11,620
But you've missed a lot of classes,
so it couldn't hurt to study.

5
00:00:12,560 --> 00:00:13,400
Oh, yeah.

6
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:14,800
He's good at studying.

7
00:00:15,620 --> 00:00:17,100
I feel kind of betrayed.

8
00:00:18,620 --> 00:00:20,400
Betrayed might be a bit much.

9
00:00:21,820 --> 00:00:23,080
Don't worry, Lady Onn.

10
00:00:23,280 --> 00:00:26,000
Even if you're not great at studying,
I'll...

11
00:00:26,540 --> 00:00:28,400
Now then, let's get to it.

12
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:30,120
What do you want me to teach you?

